value.string: A truly remarkable property– graced by a beautiful driveway at the entrance. Come and be amazed by this lovely property with unobstructed ocean views and a fabulous infinity saltwater pool. The furniture is negotiable and could be purchased on a separate bill of sale.. This property has not been cpr’d. There are three structures - a main house with a 3 car garage and maids quarters attached, a very private 2 bed 2 bath cottage and a barn (farm dwelling) with a 2 car garage. You will be pleasantly surprised by the lush tropical landscaping which rounds off the great atmosphere surrounding you upon entering this special ocean view retreat. Sellers are very motivated.

With breathtaking ocean views from almost every room, this elegant “old Hawaii style” 2,518 square-foot, 3 bedroom/3.5 bath home has just been renovated with gorgeous bamboo flooring throughout and honed granite, marble, travertine and limestone countertops plus a huge new kitchen with modern high-end stainless steel appliances. Located atop Makena Point, a bluff so prominent that a WWII pillbox was once erected there to protect nearby Makena Landing from invasion, this gracious traditional home with plantation-style details and classic open-floor plan boasts a large bay window with window seat, crown molding, telescoping doors, 3-zone air conditioning and unobstructed southern views of the Landing, Makena Bay, Molokini and neighbor island Kahoolawe. Its spacious covered lanais and upstairs wraparound deck also offer amazing views of Haleakala all the way north to Maalaea. The beautiful master bedroom and both large and airy guest bedrooms have modern en suite baths and generous tranquil outdoor sitting areas. You’ll enjoy the privacy offered by this coveted walled and gated property located on a 14,375-foot lot surrounded by lush, mature tropical landscaping including large grassy areas. Just a few steps away at Makena Landing is some of Maui's best snorkeling, diving and kayaking. And world-famous Makena Beach and Golf Resort with its fabulous restaurants, spa, golf and tennis is just a few minutes away too! Imagine this home as your island paradise!
